criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  concussion diagnosed by a physician;

          -  presence of at least one post-concussion symptom for three months or more;
             -experiencing challenges with usual daily activities secondary to post-concussive
             symptoms;

          -  able to identify four or more occupation-based goals;

          -  12-18 years of age;

          -  no concurrent serious medical or psychiatric diagnoses.

          -  has a parent who can support participation and participate in a post intervention
             interview

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  non English speaking
